│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│ │ REMINDERS [Update]                                  │ │
│ │ Upcoming appointments, tasks, alerts               │ │
│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

↓ Click "← Return to List" ↓

│ Returns to initial Dashboard view with all pet profiles │
│ Pet selector remembers Buster as active choice          │


